Troglocaris (Troglocaris)

].

Distribution: Populations west and south-west of Planinska jama, in Kras/Carso, and up to the central parts of Istra Peninsula (Labin) are related (
Zakšek et al. , 2007
). Populations in the lower reaches of the river Soča/Isonzo ( Italy ), and from the southern and western parts of the Istra Peninsula ( Croatia ), have not yet been molecularly investigated.

Other taxa:
