;
Troglocaris fagei Birštejn, 1939
;
Troglocaris osterloffi
Juzbaš’jan, 1940;
Troglocaris birsteini
Mugue, Zueva & Ershov, 2001
in Abhazetis ( Abkhazia ) in Georgia ;
Troglocaris jusbaschjani
Birštejn, 1948
in Tatarstan in Russia .
